name: Commander In Coldstar Battlesuit
legend: Capable of soaring at high speed over the battlefield, or even operating in the cold void of space, the XV86 Battlesuit is an exceptionally advanced weapon of war. It is favoured by those Commanders who seek to be everywhere at once, striking and fading wherever they are needed most.

defaultLoadout.raw: This model is equipped with: high-output burst cannon; battlesuit fists.

raw.description:
This model's high-output burst cannon can be replaced with one of the following:
  • 1 airbursting fragmentation projector*
  • 1 battlesuit support system*
  • 1 burst cannon
  • 1 cyclic ion blaster*
  • 1 fusion blaster
  • 1 missile pod
  • 1 plasma rifle
  • 1 shield generator*
  • 1 T'au flamer
  • 1 weapon support system*

This model can be equipped with up to two of the following, and can take duplicates:
  • 1 gun drone
  • 1 marker drone
  • 1 shield drone

This model can be equipped with up to three of the following, and can take duplicates:
  • 1 airbursting fragmentation projector*
  • 1 battlesuit support system*
  • 1 burst cannon
  • 1 cyclic ion blaster*
  • 1 fusion blaster
  • 1 missile pod
  • 1 plasma rifle
  • 1 shield generator*
  • 1 T'au flamer
  • 1 weapon support system*
* This model cannot have duplicates of these pieces of wargear.

abilities.name: Battlesuit Support System
abilities.description: The bearer's unit is eligible to shoot in a turn in which it Fell Back, but when doing so only models equipped with this wargear can make ranged attacks.

abilities.name: Shield Generator
abilities.description: The bearer has a 4+ invulnerable save.

abilities.name: Weapon Support System
abilities.description: Each time the bearer makes a ranged attack, you can ignore any or all modifiers to the Hit roll.

abilities.name: Coldstar Commander
abilities.description: While this model is leading a unit, models in that unit have a Move characteristic of 12" and ranged weapons equipped by models in that unit have the [ASSAULT] ability.
